e4ea76484b70bd9beb65b2964bbcff3b3f78f5f6fe70b12309a7721ca134e3735e8aaac09803f93b393a6130a703f8f346c0df89ad45d18c580dac1e0e922276  10-Revert-gdkseatdefault-Grab-touch-events-where-applic.patch"
